commit.message: Tweaking readme and travis for 3.1.7 release

Merge branch 'bitstring-3.1-update'

# Conflicts:
#	README.rst
Upping version numbers, copyright years and adding release notes.
Partial fix for find() when using LSB0. Added skeleton of some LSB0 tests that still need to be added.
Allowing initialisation with a io.BytesIO object. Issue 189.
More code tidying. Getting ready for 3.1.7 release.
Fixing Issue 201 with del not deleting everything it should in rare cases. Some general code tidying.
Fixing deprecated collections warning. Issue 193.
Fixing some of the lsb0 issues.
More LSB0 experimental code
safety lsb0
Updating documentation in package and external links to docs.
Removing PDF manual as it's usually out of date and available online.
Adding Python 3.7 and 3.8 support in setup.py
Updated link to bitstring image so it should work externally.
